donations.donation_comment: Thank you Freedom Convoy for fighting tyranny. It's no more about Conservatives versus Liberals, it's about Freedom versus Tyranny.

Thank you! To every trucker and their supporters in Ottawa and elsewhere. Standing around in freezing winter temperatures cannot be fun. I sincerely hope that the PM and the RCMP are asked by the judiciary about their  acts. You have inspired the whole world to question acts of medical and political tyranny. God bless all who had the courage to protest for humanity. I salute you from England.

GiveSendGo... thank you for honouring people's donations and giving them directly to the Freedom Convoy. Thank you for your statement: "Know this! Canada has absolutely ZERO jurisdiction over how we manage our funds here at GiveSendGo."
Disgusting behaviour by some of our government representatives, trying to freeze citizens' donations!  So very sad!
Thank you Angel truckers and the supporters who help them, carrying on your shoulders the burden of our difficult times, but protected by the Grace of God. We love you.
Thank you Truckers and thank you GiveSendGo!
Hold the line, but remember the only true Freedom is in Christ. 1 Corinthians 15:-1-8, Ephesians 2:8-10, John 3:13-18, Romans 10:8-10
